Maybe you are in debt, but a paycheck is still on the way, or perhaps you are a busy housewife, a stay-at-home father, a college student, just want to earn extra fast money to make ends meet.
No matter what your circumstances may be right now, remember one thing: “Life started getting good when I started making money”.

Today, I am going to share a list of options how to make money from home quickly. To be included on this list, the option needs to be a real legit way to make money fast. Let’s fetch these low-hanging fruits.

## 1. Take paid surveys online

[Swagbucks][swagbukslink] is a great legit survey site to earn quick money ([get $5 signup bonus now][swagbukslink]). Besides taking surveys, you will earn extra money by simply surfing the web, internet shopping, watching videos and playing games.

[Survey Junkie][surveyjunkielink] is another awesome site to take online surveys. Survey Junkie is always recruiting new members worldwide to answer surveys and test new products from a variety of companies. Most surveys will take less than 5 minutes to complete, and you will be paid about [$0.5~$1][surveyjunkielink] per survey. 

## 2. Download Apps and earn cash back

Have you ever heard about [DOSH][doshlink]? 

[DOSH][doshlink] is the latest dominating cash back App. It is available from both iOS and Android Stores and is definitely safe to use. Unlike traditional cash back Apps that people need to work with, it’s essentially a “set and forget” application. Plus, DOSH is offering free money to new users. [Sign up and get $5][doshlink] when you link your first card and another $10 for each friend that you refer (**Update**: DOSH is now only available in US).

## 3.Get paid by searching the web
Ready to make cash for doing what you do online every day? 

[Qmee][qmeelink] rewards you for searching in Google or other search engines, even Amazon. What you need to do is just installing a [simple add-on][qmeelink] to your browser. When you conduct a search there may be a few sponsored results alongside your normal search. Click them and you will get reward. The good thing is that there is no minimum to cashout. [Sign up today for free][qmeelink] and start earning from searches!

## 4. Earn money by writing

If you are serious in writing, then you should consider make money as a [freelance writer](https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Freelancer). Many websites or blogs are paying for posts from freelance writers these days. Most newbie freelance writers make anywhere from $25 to $100 for a 500 to 1,000 word article from the beginning. After a while, they generally increase their rates and many earn over 6-figures annually. [Holly Johnson][earnmorewritinglink], the owner of ClubThrifty.com, offered a splendid course to teach people how to make money as a freelance writer [from $0 to $225,000] [earnmorewritinglink] a year and there is also a [free workshop] [earnmorewritinglink] offered by her.

## 5. Make money as a proofreader

Tired of writing, just want to read? Proofreading is another legit job where you can actually earn real money. Again, this is something that you can do from almost anywhere in the world, as if you have an internet connection. 

[Proofreadanywhere][proofreadanywherelink] is now providing a course as well as a [free workshop][proofreadanywherelink] to help people learn the ways to start make money fast as a proofreader, check it out!

## 6. Get paid as a virtual assist
[Being a virtual assistant (VA)] (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Virtual_assistant) is part of making money online. VAs usually do following tasks: 1) booking travels, 2) post on social media, 3) write and respond to emails, and actually there are [150+ services you can be offered as a VA][horkeyhandbooklink]. 

[Laura Pennington][sixfigurewritingsecretslink], used to teach 7th grade middle school in Baltimore City and barely made ends meet, has now worked full-time for herself as a freelance virtual assistant from zero experience. She is now opening course,[Your Way To VA][sixfigurewritingsecretslink], to walk you through how to become a VA -- just like what she did.

## 7. Claim your forgotten money
[Unclaimed][unclaimedlink] is an interesting site that you can claim you money that you might have forgotten. It might be a paycheck that never be cashed out or some money left in an old bank account or utility deposit forgotten to be got back.

## 8. Earn money by test website
Thankfully, testing websites is a legitimate opportunity, as if you are willing to do your research and put in some actual work. Several companies, such as [UserTesting][usertestinglink] ($10 for 10~15 minutes test), [Userlytics][userlyticslink] ($5~$20 per test), [WhatUsersDo][whatusersdolink] ($8 per test), are willing to pay for your feedback, provided you have a laptop of mobile phone.

## 9. Teach English Online
Do you speak English? [VIPKID][vipkidlink] offer an opportunity to teach teens English online. You don’t need to prepare teaching materials, because their curriculum team has already designed materials for every class. Cassandra from Urbana, IL started online teaching and had no idea what to expect. Now she has been teaching for [VIPKID][vipkidlink] for 7 months already and amazed by so many personal connections with students through the internet. VIPKID paid [$14~$22 per hour] (vipkid), so easy to achieve [$500 a month] [vipkidlink] by teaching English 1 hour per day.

## 10. Earn money by reviewing music
[Slicethepie][slicethepielink] pay you to rate music from 1 ~ 10 and share your opinion on new songs before they are released. To write a good review, you don’t need much knowledge of music, just explain how it makes you feel and comparing it to the other artists/songs you already know. An average song will take three minutes and you therefore listen to ten in half an hour, you’re [looking at $5 an hour earnings] [slicethepielink]. It is not a big money, but as soon as you hit $10 you can make a cash withdrawal to your Paypal account.

## 11. Start Dropshipping Business 
[Shopify][shopifylink] enables you sell other people’s products through [Dropshipping][dropshippinglink]. Instead of investing thousands of dollars into product inventory, you can focus on the marketing, customer support and daily functions of your store and promote it by social marketing and content marketing. 

Shopify provides [free online workshops](shopifycourse) for people who are interested to start this [new business](shopifycourse).

## 12. Sell your photos
If you are creative and are good at photography, you can upload your photographs to stock websites to sell for free. A good starting point is [Shutterstock]( shutterstock), [123RF](123rf) or [Getty Images](gettyimages).

You can also make money by selling your own Instagram images on [InstaPrints](instraprints), like what [Daniel Arnold](danielarnold) has done (made over $15K in one day)! When a customer purchases one of your prints, InstaPrint will finalize all the details. Payments are usually made on the 15th of each month via PayPal.

